Body:
stacked_deck.remove_all(playing_cards.StandardPlayingCard(ranks.ACE, suits.
    SPADE))
expected_cards = [playing_cards.StandardPlayingCard(rank, suits.SPADE) for
    rank in [ranks.TEN, ranks.JACK, ranks.QUEEN, ranks.KING]]
for expected_card in expected_cards:
    assert expected_card in stacked_deck
assert stacked_deck.num_cards == 4
